<ul class="collection">
	<li class="collection-item avatar">
		<i class="material-icons circle">local_offer</i>
		<span class="title"><b>1 Ticket</b></span>
		<p>Tira un ch&iacute;charo a ver que pasa.</p>
		<a class="secondary-content waves-effect waves-light btn-small fixed-width" href="#!" onclick="apretaste.send({'command':'CREDITO PROCESAR','data':{'item':'1TICKET'}})">Canjear &sect;0.50</a>
	</li>
	<li class="collection-item avatar">
		<i class="material-icons circle">style</i>
		<span class="title"><b>5 Tickets</b></span>
		<p>Aumenta tus changes. La suerte es loca.</p>
		<a class="secondary-content waves-effect waves-light btn-small fixed-width" href="#!" onclick="apretaste.send({'command':'CREDITO PROCESAR','data':{'item':'5TICKETS'}})">Canjear &sect;2.00</a>
